      <title>诺和诺德的肾脏试验将心脏病风险和死亡降低了 24%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-ozempic-trial-delays-progression-chronic-kidney-disease-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项大型后期研究显示，诺和诺德广泛使用的糖尿病药物 Ozempic 可以延缓糖尿病患者慢性肾病的进展，将主要心脏事件和死亡的风险降低 24%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-ozempic-trial-delays-progression-chronic-kidney-disease-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:07:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
